{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, that informant is dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We killed him in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We, I mean, other people who had something against him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The minute he arrived in Auschwitz, just like everyone else, we killed him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He informed on me in the Kripo-- K-R-I-P-O-- Kripo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Kripo is short for Kriminalpolizei.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Kripo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Kriminalpolizei.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had a department in the ghetto, and they used to call in people who they suspected, or who were informed, that they know of a certain treasure that is hidden.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That either they hid it or their parents hid it, and they took you in there and gave you hearings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every day, a hearing was beating to the death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My wife's brother was called in, and I think that's what killed him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They beat the heck out of him for only one week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was there for three weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had approximately [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 12 to 15 hearings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every hearing was complete and total torture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Torturous beating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I really didn't know that my parents hid anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Finally, three weeks later, they let me out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was 3/4 dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Believe me, I was 3/4 dead, and alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And somehow, I came through it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And about 10 months later, the Kripo came to my aunt's sister's house that had the mangle on the ground floor-- it's sort of half a basement-- and they go right in there without questions.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They break the wall and sure enough, they take out stuff that I realized belonged to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Which means that my father did hide something in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but they called me to the Kripo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't call my sister, because my sister's name was not Berkenwald anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Kupermince.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
